book_title: Our Dumb Century: The Onion Presents 100 Years of Headlines from America's Finest News Source
Summary:
The staff of The Onion presents a satirical collection of mock
headlines and news stories, including an account of the Pentagon's
development of an A-bomb-resistant desk for schoolchildren
